%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.3/MLServer.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP HTTP2
    participant DP as DataPlane<br/>Inference Handler
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>S3/PVC
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP
    participant OTel as OTLP Collector

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>Auth validation
    RBAC->>REST: HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (pod-internal)
    REST->>DP: Route inference request
    DP->>Registry: Lookup model
    Registry->>Runtime: Dispatch to runtime
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>TLS encrypted

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>gRPC: gRPC/8081<br/>plaintext (pod-internal)
    gRPC->>DP: Route inference request
    DP->>Runtime: Dispatch to runtime
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>gRPC: ModelInferResponse
    gRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>TLS encrypted

    Note over Kafka,Runtime: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference (Optional)
    Kafka->>REST: Consume from mlserver-input<br/>9092/TCP
    Note right of REST: KafkaServer routes<br/>through DataPlane
    REST->>DP: Async inference
    DP->>Runtime: Dispatch
    Runtime-->>DP: Result
    DP->>Kafka: Produce to mlserver-output<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Storage,Runtime: Flow 4: Model Loading
    REST->>Registry: Load model request
    Registry->>Storage: Fetch model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 (S3) or filesystem (PVC)
    Storage-->>Registry: Model artifacts
    Registry->>Runtime: Initialize model

    Note over Prom,Metrics: Flow 5: Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082, plaintext
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over REST,OTel: Flow 6: Distributed Tracing (Optional)
    REST->>OTel: Export spans<br/>OTLP gRPC
    gRPC->>OTel: Export spans<br/>OTLP gRPC
